### OC.PowerSort API Testing
### ⚠️ AUTHENTICATION REQUIRED ⚠️
###
### These are Umbraco Backoffice APIs that require authentication.
### HTTP files don't support Umbraco's cookie-based authentication.
###
### RECOMMENDED: Use Swagger UI instead
### 1. Login to Umbraco backoffice: https://localhost:44367/umbraco
### 2. Navigate to: https://localhost:44367/umbraco/swagger/
### 3. Select "OCPower Sorting Backoffice API" from dropdown
### 4. Test endpoints directly in Swagger UI (automatically authenticated)
###
### ALTERNATIVE: Extract cookies from browser
### See instructions at bottom of this file for cookie-based authentication
###

@baseUrl = https://localhost:44367
@apiBase = {{baseUrl}}/umbraco/oc/power-sort/v1

###############################################
# SCHEDULES API
###############################################

### Get all schedules
GET {{apiBase}}/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

### Get schedules for specific parent (with query params)
GET {{apiBase}}/schedules?parentId=31523089-f648-4883-9087-ef9a0b83129f&activeOnly=false
Content-Type: application/json

### Get schedules (active only)
GET {{apiBase}}/schedules?activeOnly=true
Content-Type: application/json

### Get specific schedule by ID
GET {{apiBase}}/schedules/YOUR-SCHEDULE-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Get active schedules for parent
GET {{apiBase}}/schedules/active/YOUR-PARENT-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Create new schedule
POST {{apiBase}}/schedules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "parentId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "targetPosition": 0,
  "startDateTime": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDateTime": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "priority": 10
}

### Update schedule
PUT {{apiBase}}/schedules/YOUR-SCHEDULE-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetPosition": 1,
  "startDateTime": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDateTime": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "priority": 5
}

### Delete schedule
DELETE {{apiBase}}/schedules/YOUR-SCHEDULE-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

###############################################
# ENUM PRIORITIES API
###############################################

### Get all enum priorities
GET {{apiBase}}/enum-priorities
Content-Type: application/json

### Get enum priorities with pagination
GET {{apiBase}}/enum-priorities?skip=0&take=50
Content-Type: application/json

### Get specific enum priority by ID
GET {{apiBase}}/enum-priorities/YOUR-ENUM-PRIORITY-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Create enum priority
POST {{apiBase}}/enum-priorities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "High Priority",
  "sortPriority": 100
}

### Update enum priority
PUT {{apiBase}}/enum-priorities/YOUR-ENUM-PRIORITY-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Priority Name",
  "sortPriority": 50
}

### Delete enum priority
DELETE {{apiBase}}/enum-priorities/YOUR-ENUM-PRIORITY-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

###############################################
# CHILDREN AND SORTING API
###############################################

### Get children of a node
GET {{apiBase}}/children/YOUR-PARENT-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Sort documents
PUT {{apiBase}}/sort/document
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parent": {
    "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
  },
  "sorting": [
    {
      "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "sortOrder": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "sortOrder": 1
    }
  ]
}

###############################################
# DEFAULT SORT ORDER API
###############################################

### Get default sort order for parent
GET {{apiBase}}/default-sort-order/YOUR-PARENT-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Save current sort order as default
POST {{apiBase}}/default-sort-order/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parentId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Restore default sort order
POST {{apiBase}}/default-sort-order/restore/YOUR-PARENT-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### Clear default sort order
DELETE {{apiBase}}/default-sort-order/YOUR-PARENT-GUID-HERE
Content-Type: application/json

###############################################
# MENU ITEMS API
###############################################

### Get menu items for current user
GET {{apiBase}}/menu-items
Content-Type: application/json

### Save menu items for current user
POST {{apiBase}}/menu-items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "name": "My Favorite Page",
      "icon": "icon-home",
      "sortOrder": 0
    }
  ]
}

###############################################
# SWAGGER/OpenAPI DOCUMENTATION
###############################################

### View Swagger JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/umbraco/swagger/ocpowersorting/swagger.json
Content-Type: application/json

### View Swagger UI (Open in browser)
# https://localhost:44367/umbraco/swagger/
